==English==

===Etymology===
: (A proper name) Said to derive from the surname of Wilbur Clingan, who served with Gene Roddenberry in the Police Department.

===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|klĭng'ŏn}}, {{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɒn/}}, {{SAMPA|/"klINQn/}}
*{{IPA|/ˈklɪŋɑn/}}, {{SAMPA|/"klINAn/}}<!-- cot-caught merger or just US-style IPA? -->

===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{countable}} Member of an alien warrior race in the Star Trek universe, depicted as having distinctive forehead ridges, and a culture based on strict observance of honour, loyalty, and combat.
# {{uncountable}} Language spoken by members of that race during Star Trek movies and episodes.

